rComments: I really enjoyed this class. Shes an awesome prof who is clearly interested in the work. She gives opportunity re-submit assignments if you did poorl. Her feedback for your work is often overwhelming but she really wants to make sure people learn to write properly. She is crazy smart & I actually remember what i learned in her class. <3

My fave Prof. @ this campus. She is approachable and clearly passionate about the material. I enjoyed her lectures as they are informative, interesting, useful, and relate to everyday life. Also, she utilizes different methods of teaching (discussion, handouts, powerpoint, video clips) and evaluating. There is also the opportunity to re-submit work
